 2023-05752023-06-16CIRNAC
ActFirst Nations Jurisdiction over Education in British Columbia Act
SubjectOrder Bringing Individual Agreements with First Nations into Effect
PrecisORDER BRINGING INDIVIDUAL AGREEMENTS WITH FIRST NATIONS INTO EFFECT in order to (1) add Squamish Nation, Ditidaht First Nation, and Canim Lake to the schedule of the Act; and (2) give force of law to education jurisdiction agreements with these First Nations, thereby recognizing their jurisdiction over education for their First Nations as set out in the agreements.
